      "parameters": {
        "content": "### üì© Gmail Auto-Responder for Customer Enquiries with Knowledgebase Search\n\nThis workflow checks new emails in Gmail every minute. It classifies whether each message is a customer enquiry using a Text Classifier node. Non-enquiry emails are skipped. For enquiry emails, the AI Agent responds using only verified content pulled from a Pinecone knowledgebase.\n\nThe workflow embeds the incoming message with OpenAI and matches it to relevant data in Pinecone (FAQs namespace). The AI Agent then builds a reply using only this content. A memory node ensures conversation continuity by session ID. Responses are warm, professional, and accurate. Finally, Gmail sends the reply and adds a label to mark the thread as handled.\n",
